title: 2003 Icelandic Cup
text: The Visa-Bikar 2003 was the forty-fourth season of the <a href="Iceland">Iceland</a>ic national <a href="Association%20football">football</a> cup. It started on May 18, 2003 and concluded with the final on September 27, 2003. The winners qualified for the <a href="UEFA%20Cup%202004%E2%80%9305%23First%20qualifying%20round">first qualifying round</a> of the UEFA Cup 2004–05.
